data.description: TRANSFERRABLE 2.25% MORTGAGE RATE on this hard to find ALL BRICK executive home in a great, established community.  Inground pool with a cabana, fenced yard and 3 car garage.  Home is located about a mile from a Lake Hartwell boat ramp.  The lot is a massive .79 acres.  This home is gorgeous. 3 bedrooms on the main level, 2 full baths and a half bath, a sunroom and an office located off the master bedroom.  Master suite is oversized, it has an attached full bath with 2 vanities with a walk-in closet, seperate shower and jetted tub.  High ceilings with crown molding, chair rails and plantation shutters, gas longs and palladium windows throughout the house.  This home has so much to offer.
